stories.text:
Hello everyone!

For me, things are almost as exciting as they can get! Most of the work on BotMeNot’s initial development is close to completion!

This means that our Beta program will be going live on the 7th of December, 2021!

What’s more - for a limited time we’ll be giving away 100 free credits to everyone who signs up during the Beta testing!

I’m super thrilled to invite you to try out BotMeNot as a beta user and let me know what you think!

Register here: https://botmenot.com/beta-users-wanted/

Besides the free credits, here’s what you can expect:

Three different types of tests you can run - Starter (1 credit), Light (5 credits) & Smart (20 credits) Run tests on any website/domain - yours or someone else’s Get insights into how protected a domain is from bot traffic Get evidence of the performed tests

Got any questions? Don’t hesitate to ask!
